---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Priorities — Ball for Bloomfield">
    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="wrap"><h1>Priorities</h1></div>
    </section>

    <section class="section alt">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="card full-width" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2>Priorities for Bloomfield's Future</h2>
                <p>
                    Bloomfield works better when we work together. These priorities are based on years of listening, learning, and working alongside you to get
                    things done.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cards" style="margin-top:16px">
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Dream Together & Involve Youth</h3>
                    <p>Let's make Bloomfield a place where young people feel valued and heard - not just included, but invited.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Add a youth representative to the Parks & Recreation Board</li>
                        <li>Create regular forums where students can share ideas about Bloomfield's future</li>
                        <li>Ask young people directly: what would make you want to build your future here?</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Downtown Development</h3>
                    <p>Our downtown square is more vibrant and better occupied than it was a decade ago. Let's keep building on what works.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Support businesses that are investing in the square</li>
                        <li>Continue the city-Main Street partnerships that have proven successful</li>
                        <li>Encourage sidewalk cafés, weekend events, and improved walkability</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Housing & Community Development</h3>
                    <p>Bloomfield needs more housing options for families, seniors, and workers.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encourage infill development in existing neighborhoods</li>
                        <li>Support a mix of housing types that serves our community</li>
                        <li>
                            Evaluate Lake Fisher improvements including recreation upgrades, trails connecting to the city, and potential housing while being
                            good stewards of the public resource
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Strong Infrastructure</h3>
                    <p>
                        We need to modernize electric, water, sewer, and natural gas systems using state and federal funding so we stop wasting money on
                        outdated equipment.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Upgrade aging electrical infrastructure to improve reliability and efficiency</li>
                        <li>Sequence water and sewer upgrades to minimize disruption</li>
                        <li>Evaluate the condition and investment needs of the city's natural gas utility</li>
                        <li>Use grant-writing experience to access infrastructure funding</li>
                        <li>Work with technical partners like Iowa State University and Iowa Economic Development Authority (IEDA)</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Efficiency & Resilience</h3>
                    <p>Small towns can plan smart, stretch dollars, and take the long view.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Use grants and partnerships to reduce pressure on property taxes</li>
                        <li>Make efficiency improvements that save money long-term</li>
                        <li>Plan for resilience against storms and emergencies</li>
                        <li>Support practical tools like the expanded tool library</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Business Growth</h3>
                    <p>
                        Make it easier for employers and entrepreneurs to succeed in Bloomfield - whether they're on the square, in industrial areas, or
                        starting something new.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Support existing businesses with practical help, not bureaucracy</li>
                        <li>Explore options for industrial park improvements</li>
                        <li>Modernize zoning and permitting processes</li>
                        <li>Encourage the mix of businesses that creates good jobs</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
